1. *Čitam* knjigu već dva sata. (I am reading a book for two hours already.)
2. On *čita* novine svako jutro. (He reads the newspaper every morning.)
3. Kada si *pročitala* ovu knjigu? (When did you read this book?)
4. *Čitajte* ovaj tekst polako. (Read this text slowly.)
5. Prošle nedelje nisam imao vremena da *pročitam* novine. (Last week I didn't have time to read the newspaper.)
6. Na fakultetu sam *čitala* dosta knjiga o toj temi. (In college, I read a lot of books on that topic.)
7. *Čitao* sam knjigu celu noć. (I read the book all night.)
8. Da li *čitaš* na srpskom jeziku? (Do you read in Serbian?)
9. Naučila sam *čitati* kada sam imala pet godina. (I learned to read when I was five years old.)
10. Molim te da mi *pročitaš* ovo pismo. (Please read this letter to me.)